title: Board Meeting Rebroadcasts on KLCS (Los Angeles Unified School District)
text: ( Source : Los Angeles Unified School District ) This week's LAUSD Board of Education meeting will be rebroadcast on KLCS Sunday, Oct. 25 during the following times: LAUSD Committee Meeting: Starts at 7 a.m. (3 hour 8 minutes run time) LAUSD
